<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id6c012b47-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e" identifier="/us/usc/t33/s1373"><num value="1373">§ 1373.</num><heading> Public health agency coordination</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The permitting agency under <ref href="/us/usc/t33/s1342">section 1342 of this title</ref> shall assist the applicant for a permit under such section in coordinating the requirements of this chapter with those of the appropriate public health agencies.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id6c012b48-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e">(<ref href="/us/act/1948-06-30/ch758">June 30, 1948, ch. 758</ref>, title V, § 514, as added <ref href="/us/pl/92/500/s2">Pub. L. 92–500, § 2</ref>, <date date="1972-10-18">Oct. 18, 1972</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/86/894">86 Stat. 894</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
